# Executando o Projeto

## Clonar repositГіrio

```bash
git clone https://github.com/seu-usuario/api-gateway.git
```

## Entrar na pasta

```bash
cd api-gateway
```

## Executar

Linux:

```bash
./mvnw spring-boot:run
```

Windows:

```bash
mvnw.cmd spring-boot:run
```

Ou:

```bash
mvn clean package
java -jar target/api-gateway.jar
```

